## ðŸ§ª Running Playwright Tests

1. **Install Playwright and its browsers:**
   ```sh
   npm install --save-dev playwright
   npx playwright install
   ```

2. **Run all Playwright tests:**
   ```sh
   npx playwright test
   ```

3. **View the HTML test report:**
   ```sh
   npx playwright show-report
   ```

> Playwright tests are located in the `tests`folder.  
> The GitHub Actions workflow will automatically run these tests on every push or pull request.
